@startuml State Diagram - Route Status
[*] --> processing : Route created

processing --> processing : Photo upload in progress
processing --> partial : Some photos uploaded\n(pointsWithPhotos > 0 && < totalPoints)
processing --> complete : All photos uploaded\n(pointsWithPhotos == totalPoints)

partial --> partial : More photos uploaded
partial --> complete : All photos uploaded\n(pointsWithPhotos == totalPoints)

complete --> [*] : Route completed

note right of processing
    Initial status when route is created
    No photos uploaded yet
end note

note right of partial
    Some points have photos
    Route is partially processed
end note

note right of complete
    All points have photos
    Route processing finished
end note
@enduml
